@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

title Pendle PT Risk-Oracle Workflow on Chainlink CRE

|Data inputs|
start
:Pendle AMM price;
:Parameter registry\n(per-asset config for every\nasset with a PT price feed);

|CRE workflow (protocol-owned)|
:Load inputs into workflow;
:Run risk methodology\n(evaluate threshold conditions);
if (Optimisation identified?) then (yes)
  :Compute risk-managed price\n+ liquidation parameters;
  |On-chain|
  :CRE pushes value via\nLlama Guard oracle;
  :Authorise updates to\ntarget Aave market\n+ market oracle;
  stop
else (no)
  |CRE workflow (protocol-owned)|
  :No update pushed;
  stop
endif
@enduml
